should we risk the pilots?

2275
02:05:36,363 --> 02:05:39,066
Men dying is a relative thing.

2276
02:05:39,100 --> 02:05:41,869
The effect of the air
campaign is cumulative.

2277
02:05:41,903 --> 02:05:44,772
Every blow makes the enemy
stretch his resources.

2278
02:05:44,806 --> 02:05:46,974
Stretching is a relative thing.

2279
02:05:47,008 --> 02:05:49,911
Mr. President, we shouldn't be
bombing for punitive reasons,

2280
02:05:49,944 --> 02:05:51,454
but there just doesn't seem
any point to this anymore!

2281
02:05:51,478 --> 02:05:53,014
Hit it!

2282
02:05:53,047 --> 02:05:54,681
Hit the goddamn bridge.

2283
02:05:54,715 --> 02:05:56,750
What's next?

2284
02:05:56,784 --> 02:06:00,955
Number 309, sir, the, railcar repair shop.

2285
