Stop the war in Vietnam!

2315
02:09:09,743 --> 02:09:12,246
Bring the troops home now!

2316
02:09:12,279 --> 02:09:14,982
Let's go! Let's go!
File in, move it up!

2317
02:09:15,016 --> 02:09:16,950
